data.description: Your Dream Home Awaits!  Step into this stunning 2020-built gem nestled in the heart of Central Gainesville. This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is a testament to modern design and comfort.  Property Highlights: Custom-designed with an open kitchen, perfect for gatherings and entertaining friends. High-quality finishes and top-notch features throughout, ensuring luxury and style in every corner. A thoughtfully designed split floor plan that offers maximum privacy, making it ideal for professionals and individuals alike.  Prime Location: Convenience is at your doorstep with this fantastic location! Just minutes away from HWY 441 and I-75, your daily commute to Shands, VA Hospital, UF, and shopping centers will be a breeze. Say goodbye to long hours on the road!  Home Features:  4 spacious bedrooms, offering ample space for your lifestyle. 2.5 beautifully appointed bathrooms for your comfort.  Expansive living areas bathed in natural light. Modern kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances and plenty of counter space. Cozy backyard, perfect for outdoor relaxation and play. Perfect for Professionals and Individuals: Whether you're a busy professional seeking a convenient location or an individual looking for comfort and style, this property has it all. Nearby shopping centers, excellent schools, and easy access to major highways make this the perfect place to call home. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Schedule a viewing today and discover the home of your dreams. Your forever home awaits you! ??
